EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0600Z TO 2000Z DAILY

   32 MILES OF 57-15.9N 008-28.3W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA

   ON VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449
   FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 262100Z JUL 17.
